  "time_ut": 1657444224,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dcf \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith condemns the burning of the Prime Minister's house",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the leader of the opposition, says that he condemns with contempt the burning of the house of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe by some subversive group.",
        "In a statement, the opposition leader stressed that a fair investigation should be conducted against all those involved in the incident and punishment should be given regardless of rank.",
        "\"We firmly believe that the entire people of this country joined a civil struggle for a society governed by democracy, human rights and justice, and they were disciplined and civilized enough to never betray its noble goals.",
        "But under the guise of that struggle, we are unconditionally opposed to property destruction, arson and minor events that confuse people's lives by some opportunistic and disruptive groups.",
        "In the last few days, a large number of people including activists, journalists, civil citizens also had to face violence and we emphasize that extensive investigations should be conducted in this regard."
      ],
